    <measure>Change in mean urine volume</measure>
    <time_frame>Baseline, 7 hours</time_frame>
    <description>Urine volume is a measure of fluid balance. Change from baseline in average volume of urine collected from baseline to 7 hours.</description>
  </secondary_outcome>
